   ! Rebuild the DIIS left hand side matrix, "lhs", using the error vectors on
   ! disk. The "lhs" matrix is saved to disk. Also, resets the index ".new".
   ! "e_i" and "e_j" are used as workspace; whatever is in them is trashed.
   end

